          <p class="lead">A practical guide to choosing and using payment apps and transfer services (PayPal, Wise, Stripe, Revolut, bank transfers, local wallets) to receive and send money securely, cheaply, and fast — optimized for online sellers, freelancers, and SaaS businesses.</p>

          <div class="chips" aria-hidden="true">
